===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ja|en}} {{term|漢字|tr=kanji||Chinese characters}}, from {{etyl|ltc|en}} 漢 (''xàn'' "Han dynasty", "China") + 字 (''dzì'' "[written] character") (compare {{etyl|ko|en}} ''hanja'' 한자, {{etyl|cmn|en}} ''hànzi'' 汉子, {{etyl|vi|en}} ''Hán tự'').

===Pronunciation===
